710799f-a.text:
Twelfth Ave., east side, at West 56th Street, showing under construction the new incinerator building of the Dept. of Sanitation, on the S.E. corner
of West 56th Street.
May 21, 1936.
L Sperr.

710800f-a.text:
Twelfth Ave., east side, north from West 56th Street. Note on the left the elevated West Side Vehicular Express Highway.
November 23, 1936.
W.P.A. Photo.
Federal Art Project.
